snippet.title: GORN 2 | ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER
snippet.description: GORN 2 is the skull-crushing sequel to VR smash hit GORN. New developers Cortopia, working alongside original series creators Free Lives, are stepping into the arena to take on virtual reality’s most outrageous gladiator sim.
